---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Third-party components installed by the SofaControl setup
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

SofaControl relies on two open-source drivers by Nefarius Software Solutions.
They are redistributed unmodified by the SofaControl installer:

* ViGEmBus  - Virtual Gamepad Emulation Bus driver (Xbox 360 emulation)
              https://github.com/nefarius/ViGEmBus   (BSD-3-Clause)

* HidHide   - Hides the physical controller from games so only SofaControl
              reads it.
              https://github.com/nefarius/HidHide    (BSD-3-Clause)

ViGEmClient (statically linked into SofaControl.exe) is also BSD-3-Clause,
Copyright (c) Nefarius Software Solutions e.U.
